<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Appointment Reminder</title>
    <style>
        body {
            font-family: 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
            background-color: #f5f7fa;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            color: #333;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .container {
            max-width: 600px;
            margin: 20px auto;
            background: white;
            border-radius: 10px;
            overflow: hidden;
            box-shadow: 0 5px 15px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
        }

        .header {
            background: #4a6fa5;
            padding: 25px;
            text-align: center;
            color: white;
        }

        .logo {
            height: 50px;
            margin-bottom: 10px;
        }

        .church-name {
            font-size: 22px;
            font-weight: 700;
            margin: 5px 0;
            letter-spacing: 0.5px;
        }

        .content {
            padding: 30px;
        }

        h1 {
            color: #2c3e50;
            font-size: 24px;
            margin-top: 0;
            margin-bottom: 20px;
        }

        .reminder-box {
            background: #f8f9fa;
            border-left: 4px solid #4a6fa5;
            padding: 20px;
            margin: 25px 0;
            border-radius: 0 5px 5px 0;
        }

        .detail-row {
            margin-bottom: 12px;
            display: flex;
        }

        .detail-label {
            font-weight: 600;
            min-width: 120px;
            color: #4a6fa5;
        }

        .action-buttons {
            margin: 25px 0;
            text-align: center;
        }

        .btn {
            display: inline-block;
            padding: 12px 25px;
            background: #4a6fa5;
            color: white;
            text-decoration: none;
            border-radius: 5px;
            font-weight: 600;
            margin: 0 10px;
        }

        .btn-outline {
            background: transparent;
            border: 2px solid #4a6fa5;
            color: #4a6fa5;
        }

        .footer {
            background: #2c3e50;
            color: white;
            padding: 20px;
            text-align: center;
            font-size: 13px;
        }

        .footer a {
            color: #a3c4ff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        .location {
            margin-top: 15px;
            padding-top: 15px;
            border-top: 1px dashed #ddd;
        }

        @media only screen and (max-width: 600px) {
            .container {
                margin: 0;
                border-radius: 0;
            }

            .btn {
                display: block;
                margin: 10px 0;
            }

            .detail-row {
                flex-direction: column;
            }

            .detail-label {
                margin-bottom: 5px;
            }
        }
    </style>
</head>

<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <!-- Replace with your church logo -->
            <img src="/source//public/fg-logo.jpg" alt="Church Logo" class="logo">
            <div class="church-name">Ethiopian Full Gospel Believers Church <br>
                (Silver Spring Local)
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="content">
            <h1>Appointment Reminder</h1>

            <p>Dear <%= fullName %>,</p>

            <p>This is a friendly reminder about your upcoming appointment with us. We're looking forward to connecting
                with you!</p>

            <div class="reminder-box">
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Date & Time:</div>
                    <div>
                        <%= preferredDateTime %>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="detail-row">
                    <div class="detail-label">Meeting Type:</div>
                    <div>
                        <%= medium==='in-person' ? 'In-Person Meeting' : 'Online Meeting' %>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <% if (medium==='in-person' ) { %>
                    <div class="location">
                        <div class="detail-row">
                            <div class="detail-label">Location:</div>
                            <div>Ethiopian Full Gospel Believers Church<br>
                                914 Silver Spring Ave, Suite 204 B, Silver Spring, MD 20910, USA<br>
                                (Main Office, Room 201)</div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="detail-row">
                            <div class="detail-label">Parking:</div>
                            <div>Visitor parking available in the west lot</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <% } else { %>
                        <div class="location">
                            <div class="detail-row">
                                <div class="detail-label">Meeting Link:</div>
                                <div><a href="<%= meetingLink || '#' %>">Click to join online meeting</a></div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="detail-row">
                                <div class="detail-label">Instructions:</div>
                                <div>Please join 5 minutes early to test your audio/video</div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <% } %>
            </div>

            <div class="action-buttons">
                <a href="<%= rescheduleLink || '#' %>" class="btn btn-outline">Reschedule Appointment</a>
                <a href="<%= cancelLink || '#' %>" class="btn btn-outline">Cancel Appointment</a>
            </div>

            <p>If you have any questions or need assistance, please don't hesitate to reply to this email or call us at
                (240) 821-0361.</p>

            <p>Blessings,<br>
                <strong>The Pastoral Care Team</strong><br>
                Ethiopian Full Gospel Believers Church<br>
                (Silver Spring Local)
            </p>
            </p>
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="footer">
            <div style="margin-bottom: 10px;">
                Ethiopian Full Gospel Believers Church (Silver Spring Local)<br>
                914 Silver Spring Ave, Suite 204 B, Silver Spring, MD 20910, USA
            </div>
            <div>
                <a href="mailto:office@efgbcssl.org">office@efgbcssl.org</a> |
                <a href="tel:+12408210361">(240) 821-0361</a> |
                <a href="https://efgbcssl.org">efgbcssl.org</a>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>

</html>